         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:kolver1965"/><citedRange>15, 43</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>151</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">Die eigenen Leiden hast du ertragen, und weder hast du abgelassen noch hast du Ersättigung gefunden [bzw. bist du bedrückt gewesen].</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">[Your] own sufferings you have endured, and neither have you relented nor have you found saturation [or: have you been despondent].</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>159</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3 #a4"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:hackstein1995"/><citedRange>296</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>151</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:kolver1965"/><citedRange>101</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a5"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>151</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:knoll1996"/><citedRange>73</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">Das vorzügliche Buch Maitreyasamiti haben wir geschrieben für alle ...</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">The excellent book Maitreyasamiti we have written for all ...</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>456</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b3"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:kolver1965"/><citedRange>142</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... from the suffering of the three bad incarnations ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b5"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1970"/><citedRange>268</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1983"/><citedRange>31, 37</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:kolver1965"/><citedRange>82</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">releasing from all Saṃsāra sufferings ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b7"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>421</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
